<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chong Ning Xin - Profile</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #0d9488;
            --primary-hover: #0f766e;
            --bg-color: #f8fafc;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #1e293b;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .profile-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            max-width: 650px;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.01);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .profile-img {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 4px solid var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .subtitle {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ccfbf1;
            color: #115e59;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .about-text {
            text-align: left;
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .about-text p {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .skills-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        .skill-tag {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .linkedin-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background-color: #0a66c2;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .linkedin-btn:hover {
            background-color: #004182;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .linkedin-btn svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            fill: currentColor;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <main class="profile-card">
        <!-- Profile Image -->
        <img src="/images/ningxin.jpg" alt="Chong Ning Xin" class="profile-img">

        <!-- Name & Status -->
        <h1>Chong Ning Xin</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Cybersecurity & Digital Forensics Student</div>

        <!-- About Me Section -->
        <section class="about-text">
            <p>Hello! My name is Chong Ning Xin. I am currently a Year 2 student at Republic Polytechnic’s School of Infocom, pursuing a diploma in Cybersecurity and Digital Forensics.</p>
            
            <p>My retail background as a clothes and phone sales promoter taught me the vital importance of customer relations and sharpened my communication skills. Working with mobile devices introduced me to foundational IT concepts like RAM and electronics, which ultimately sparked my passion for cybersecurity.</p>
            
            <p>I am hardworking, dedicated to my studies, and constantly eager to learn. I actively participate in networking events to connect with industry professionals and expand my skills.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Skill Tags (Added for extra flair) -->
        <div class="skills-grid">
            <span class="skill-tag">Cybersecurity</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Digital Forensics</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Customer Relations</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Hardware Basics</span>
            <span class="skill-tag">Networking</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Styled LinkedIn Link -->
        <a href="<%= typeof linkedinUrl !== 'undefined' ? linkedinUrl : 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/ning-xin-chong-664728362' %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="linkedin-btn">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M19 3a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14m-.5 15.5v-5.3a3.26 3.26 0 0 0-3.26-3.26c-.85 0-1.84.52-2.28 1.3v-1.11h-2.79v8.37h2.79v-4.93c0-.77.62-1.4 1.39-1.4a1.4 1.4 0 0 1 1.4 1.4v4.93h2.75M6.88 8.56a1.68 1.68 0 0 0 1.68-1.68c0-.93-.75-1.69-1.68-1.69a1.69 1.69 0 0 0-1.69 1.69c0 .93.76 1.68 1.69 1.68m1.39 9.94v-8.37H5.5v8.37h2.77z"/>
            </svg>
            Connect on LinkedIn
        </a>
    </main>

</body>
</html>